'''埃梅拉·恩图卡'''（Emela Ntouka）是一种生活于[[非洲|非洲]][[刚果|刚果]][[利夸拉省|利夸拉]]的[[神秘生物列表|神秘生物]]，它的名字在[[林加拉语|林格拉语]]中意为“大象杀手“（killer of the elephants）。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.genesispark.com/exhibits/evidence/cryptozoological/ceratopsian/emela-ntouka/|title=“Emela-ntouka” of the Congo|accessdate=2017年|author=|date=|publisher=|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926015056/https://www.genesispark.com/exhibits/evidence/cryptozoological/ceratopsian/emela-ntouka/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
